      <textAnnotation id="sid-E15591F7-3BA0-4FF1-A9F0-EA744F7D93CC" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: Procure To Pay
Process Group: Procure Materials and Services (Direct &amp; Indirect)
Process: PM-040-020 Communicate Requirements to Suppliers</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0B51747B-923E-476B-9FF4-E316A324686D" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>L3 Description-
Communicate standards, qualification, evaluation, and auditing procedures for the requested purchase(s) to candidate suppliers. Educate suppliers periodically about the company’s standards and requirements. These communications would include the commercial aspects of the relationship as well as volume, price, purchase order specification etc.., Communication must be forma; the vendor must accept(in writing) the standards and requirements under which they agree conduct business</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B0DC22F6-A4D4-4305-B25D-84251EAD46EC" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>-Bapp/Platform: Supplier.intel.com - New potential suppliers and existing supplier and public communication
-Supplier mass communication Ex., Annual supplier newsletter (Bapp: Poppulo)
-Social responsibility deliverables (Bapp: Graphite, suppliersoft, email)
-Supplier training (Bapp: docebo)
-2-way supplier communication (Bapp:  Graphite)
-RFx execution (Bapp:  Ariba Sourcing)
-Contract T&amp;C’s, Redline (Bapp:  iCertis)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-69D1D6BB-88C7-4EB6-90CC-011A8304C24E" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Dhanwantry, Kalyan R &lt;kalyan.r.dhanwantry@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
